			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002314_0001"/><!--pb/@n='91r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Burnbank Road</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hamilton</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">26 May 1865 </p>
<lb/><p>Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Alington</persName></p>
<lb/><p>We cannot always 
<lb/>follow our own 
<lb/>inclinations and 
<lb/>often that path 
<lb/>we would prefer 
<lb/>is not the best. 
<lb/>I should have liked 
<lb/>your company 
<lb/>I think, and this 
<lb/>I cannot say of 
<lb/>anyone else <persName><unclear cert="low">Col O</unclear></persName>
<lb/>has offered - I am 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002314_0002"/><!--pb/@n='91v'-->
<lb/>just writing a refusal 
<lb/>to an offer from 
<lb/>a Scotch doctor 
<lb/>who says he can 
<lb/>refer to the highest 
<lb/>authorities. One 
<lb/>of these being a 
<lb/>character after a 
<lb/>previous trial 
<lb/>I suspect he 
<lb/>cannot adduce 
<lb/>so I decline to have 
<lb/>him. </p>
<lb/><p>I should like 
<lb/>the cot very well 
<lb/>if very strong 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002314_0003"/><!--pb/@n='92r'-->
<lb/>and all the more 
<lb/>as coming from 
<lb/>one for whom 
<lb/>I entertain feelings 
<lb/>of sincere esteem - 
<lb/>- strength not 
<lb/>beauty, or rather 
<lb/>strength is the 
<lb/>chief quality 
<lb/>required, beauty - 
<lb/>though an advantage 
<lb/>is not so necessary<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002314_0004"/><!--pb/@n='92v'-->
<lb/><p>My point for 
<lb/>collecting luggage 
<lb/>at before starting 
<lb/>is, <placeName>19 Bucklesbury 
<lb/>London </placeName><persName> M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Brown</persName>the agent 
<lb/>there takes care 
<lb/>of my things<reg>.</reg></p><!--Mike it's also n="93r", which do we use??--><!-- I need to see the images to make sure since I can't guarantee that the envelope is even 93r until I see it.-->

	<pb n="0005" facs="liv_002314_0005"/><!--pb/@n='92a'-->
 <addSpan spanTo="#addEnd-92a"><!--addSpan/@place='Envelope'--></addSpan>
